comment.body:
@micheleselea Please ask questions about demos in this subproject.

Then, please read the documentation. I do agree that the answer to your problem is (only) documented in the README.md and not in USAGE.md where it arguably (also) belongs. 

I'd be very glad if you'd take a few minutes to go through both documents to find the solution (hint: it has to do with the default groups). If I could then convince you to create a PR with a user's perspective (i.e., updating the httpd/USAGE.md file) I'd be very happy indeed.
